      "title": "副腎偶発腫、どこまで精査する？",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "CTで偶然見つかった副腎腫瘤の精査フローチャート",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:540px;padding:0 60px;gap:60px}.left-panel{flex:1}.right-panel{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center}h1{font-size:48px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:20px}.subtitle{font-size:24px;opacity:0.85;line-height:1.6}.tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:8px 20px;border-radius:20px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;margin-right:8px}.avatar-circle{width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;border:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}.avatar-circle img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}.author-name{font-size:24px;font-weight:700}.author-title{font-size:16px;opacity:0.8;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;margin-top:4px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 1 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"left-panel\"><h1>副腎偶発腫<br>どこまで精査する？</h1><div class=\"subtitle\">CTで偶然見つかった副腎腫瘤の<br>精査フローチャート</div><div><span class=\"tag\">内分泌</span><span class=\"tag\">副腎</span><span class=\"tag\">ガイドライン</span></div></div><div class=\"right-panel\"><div class=\"avatar-circle\"><img src=\"/dr-iwatatsu.png\" alt=\"Dr.いわたつ\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"></div><div class=\"author-name\">Dr.いわたつ</div><div class=\"author-title\">糖尿病専門医・指導医<br>内分泌専門医 / 医学博士</div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 2,
      "title": "CTレポートに「副腎腫瘤」と書いてあったら？",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "起：研修医が遭遇する「あるある」問題",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:30px}.alert-box{border-left:6px solid #14b8a6;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);padding:30px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-bottom:24px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:24px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 2 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>CTレポートに「副腎腫瘤」と書いてあったら？</h2><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>腹部CTで偶然発見された副腎腫瘤<br>経過観察？ホルモン検査？外科紹介？<br>CT検査の約4%に見つかる、ありふれた所見です</p></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>約半数は非機能性腺腫で問題なし<br>しかし残りの半数には精査が必要な疾患が潜んでいます<br>褐色細胞腫8.5% / コルチゾール産生腺腫10.5% / 副腎皮質癌2-5%</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 3,
      "title": "画像診断：CT値で良悪性を見分ける",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "承：エビデンスに基づく画像評価",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.card{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 30px;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.card-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:8px}.card-body{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.highlight{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.source{font-size:18px;color:#64748b;margin-top:16px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 3 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>画像診断：CT値で良悪性を見分ける</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">良性腺腫を示唆</div><div class=\"card-body\">単純CT値 <span class=\"highlight\">10HU以下</span>（感度71%・特異度98%）<br>ESE 2023：サイズにかかわらず<span class=\"highlight\">追加画像フォロー不要</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">造影CTのwashout解析</div><div class=\"card-body\">絶対的washout率 <span class=\"highlight\">60%以上</span> → 良性腺腫<br>相対的washout率 <span class=\"highlight\">40%以上</span> → 良性腺腫</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">悪性を疑う所見</div><div class=\"card-body\">腫瘍径 <span class=\"highlight\">4cm以上</span> / CT値 <span class=\"highlight\">20HU超</span> / 不均一<br>境界不明瞭 / 壊死・出血・石灰化</div></div><div class=\"source\">出典：ESE/ENSAT Guideline, Eur J Endocrinol 2023; 189(1): G1-G42</div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 4,
      "title": "ホルモン精査：全例必須の2つの検査",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "転：画像が良性でもホルモン精査は省略できない",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:24px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:18px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6;min-width:50px;margin-right:16px}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:20px 30px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 4 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>ホルモン精査：全例必須の検査</h2><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><span class=\"list-text\">1mg overnight DST（デキサメタゾン抑制試験）<br>カットオフ：コルチゾール 1.8μg/dL 以下で正常<br>1.8超〜5以下 → MACS疑い / 5超 → クッシング疑い</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><span class=\"list-text\">血漿遊離メタネフリン分画 or 24時間尿中メタネフリン<br>褐色細胞腫の除外（35%は無症候性、見逃すと致命的）</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><span class=\"list-text\">高血圧合併例 → アルドステロン/レニン比（ARR）を追加<br>原発性アルドステロン症の除外</span></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>画像で良性に見えてもホルモン精査は省略できません</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 5,
      "title": "MACS（軽度自律性コルチゾール分泌）の管理",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "結：MACSの臨床的意義と手術適応",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;gap:30px;align-items:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:20px}.col{flex:1}.card{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.card-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:8px}.card-body{font-size:24px;line-height:1.5;color:#334155}.highlight{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 5 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"col\"><h2>MACSとは</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">旧称：サブクリニカルクッシング</div><div class=\"card-body\">有病率：副腎偶発腫の<span class=\"highlight\">5〜30%</span><br>顕性クッシングへの進展は<span class=\"highlight\">1%未満</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">合併症リスク上昇</div><div class=\"card-body\">糖尿病・高血圧・脂質異常症の有病率が<br><span class=\"highlight\">15〜40%高い</span><br>骨粗鬆症性骨折リスクも上昇</div></div></div><div style=\"width:2px;background:#14b8a6;height:80%;opacity:0.3\"></div><div class=\"col\"><h2>手術適応（ESE 2023）</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">以下の3条件を全て満たす場合</div><div class=\"card-body\">1. DST後コルチゾール <span class=\"highlight\">>5μg/dL</span><br>2. 関連合併症が<span class=\"highlight\">2つ以上</span><br>3. うち1つ以上が内科的治療で<span class=\"highlight\">不十分</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">手術しない場合</div><div class=\"card-body\">合併症の治療最適化<br><span class=\"highlight\">2〜4年</span>の内分泌フォローアップ</div></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 6,
      "title": "Take Home Message",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "3つの持ち帰りポイント",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px}.thm-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 36px;margin-bottom:24px;display:flex;align-items:center}.thm-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-right:24px;min-width:50px;opacity:0.7}.thm-text{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.5}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 6 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>Take Home Message</h2><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">01</span><span class=\"thm-text\">全例に1mg DST + メタネフリン測定<br>画像で良性でもホルモン精査は省略できない</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">02</span><span class=\"thm-text\">CT値10HU以下の均一腫瘤 → 画像フォロー不要（ESE 2023）<br>ただし4cm超・不均一・20HU超は手術を考慮</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">03</span><span class=\"thm-text\">褐色細胞腫の35%は無症候性<br>「症状がないから大丈夫」は通用しない</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 7,
      "title": "参考文献",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "論文引用",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.ref-item{margin-bottom:14px}.ref-num{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.ref-text{font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;color:#334155}.ref-url{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;word-break:break-all}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 7 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>参考文献</h2><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">1)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">Fassnacht M, et al. ESE clinical practice guidelines on the management of adrenal incidentalomas. Eur J Endocrinol 2023; 189(1): G1-G42</span><br><span class=\"ref-url\">https://doi.org/10.1093/ejendo/lvad066</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">2)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">日本内分泌学会. 副腎性サブクリニカルクッシング症候群 新診断基準. 日内分泌会誌 2019; 108(10)</span><br><span class=\"ref-url\">https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/naika/108/10/108_2148/_pdf</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">3)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">日本泌尿器科学会. 内分泌非活性副腎腫瘍診療ガイドライン 2022年版. メディカルレビュー社 2022</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">4)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">Deutschbein T, et al. Mild autonomous cortisol secretion: pathophysiology, comorbidities and management approaches. Nat Rev Endocrinol 2024; 20(8): 460-471</span><br><span class=\"ref-url\">https://doi.org/10.1038/s41574-024-00981-1</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">5)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">日本内分泌学会. 褐色細胞腫・パラガングリオーマ診療ガイドライン 2025</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
